Encoding => One-hot  
            Label
            Frequency
            Target
            Ordinal

Frequency encoding => Takrorlanishlar sonini umumiy elementlar soniga nisbati.              

airport_type => small             airport_type_freq => 0.5
                large                                  1/6
                small                                  0.5
                medium                                 2/6
                medium                                 2/6
                small                                  0.5
                ...                                    ...

Target encoding (mean) => mos target qiymatning o'rta arifmetigi. 


airport_type => small      Good (target) => 0               airport_type_target => 1/3
                large                       1                                      1
                small                       0                                      1/3
                medium                      1                                      1
                medium                      1                                      1
                small                       1                                      1/3
                ...                         ...                                    ...

airport_type ustunidagi bir xil classdagi elementlarning mos target elementlarini hisoblaymiz. Masalan: small => 0 + 0 + 1 / 3 => 1/3
large => 1 / 1 => 1   medium => 1 + 1 / 2 => 1


Ordinal encoding => Ketma ketlik ga qarab sonlar bilan almashtiriladi.

airport_type => small               airport_type_ordinal => 1      
                large                                       3
                small                                       1
                medium                                      2
                medium                                      2
                small                                       1
                ...                                         ...



For loop => Jarayonni avtomatlashtirish uchun ishlatilinadigan kodlar bloki.

Bizda so'zlar listi mavjud. str=["small", "large", "large", "medium"]. Biz har birini ekranga chiqarmoqchi bolsak quyidagi kodni ishlatamiz.

print[0]
print[1]
print[2]
print[3] 

Agar biz buni for loop orqali qilsak bu jarayonni avtomatlashtirgan bolamiz.

for i in str:
    print(i)
                
